## Philosophy

I believe that AI should be developed responsibly and ethically. Technology should augment human capabilities, not replace human judgment. I'm committed to:

- Building fair and unbiased AI systems
- Making AI accessible and understandable
- Contributing to open-source communities
- Continuous learning and skill development
- Mentoring the next generation of AI engineers

